org.sql: SELECT boards.* FROM boards INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = boards.project_id WHERE boards.project_id = "$1" AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'boards') IS NOT NULL AND projects.is_public = True AND projects.id NOT IN (SELECT project_id FROM members WHERE user_id IN (6, 13)) AND boards.name = "$2" ORDER BY boards.position ASC LIMIT 1
